reviews.review_text: AMAZING SET! Brent Mydland!!! Goin down the road feelin GREAT! Wonderfully Amazing Althea "there are some you can replace, and others you cannot!!" THANKS FOR SHARING!

Loose with the truth.. Good sound with a bit of hiss..Pure magic in Germany with Brent Bells and yes... the Althea is off the Hook!!!!  start to finish..so please >>GIVE IT A WHIRL!! Forever Grateful>Forever Dead@!@!@!
on this night Many of us go to the oooops shows of the 15 th and 16 th , yet this show here they are firing on all cylinders. Wow holy Going down the road.
